title: Worst Date Wednesday: She was drunk on the bathroom floor
description: Barbara calls to tell us how she was the worst date. It all started when she found out her brother that she's really close with was eloping and not including her.  She started drinking and then proceeded to still go on a date she had planned which led to the bartender having to check on her in the bathroom.
